        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://iandallas.com/games/swan/">The Unfinished Swan</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Video preview of a really interesting looking new indie game where the world is completely blank until you fire at it with your one weapon: A paintball gun which helps you &#8220;see&#8221; the obstacles.  Watch the video to see it make sense.</p>

